description: Seeks to track the performance of the CRSP US Total Market Index to the extent possible and before fees and expenses. Invests primarily in the U.S.-domiciled Vanguard Total Stock Market ETF. Employs a passively managed, index-sampling strategy to provide exposure to large-, mid-, small- and micro-capitalizations. U.S. public equities diversified across growth and value styles. Uses efficient, cost-effective index management techniques.
name: Vanguard U.S. Total Market Index ETF
